msgstr "检测玩家生命值变化时刻"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:14 1ee9e6ead6ff484f9c6170f853b6d6e5
msgid "Find all other players who are linked to that player"
msgstr "查找所有关联玩家"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:15 950a6078b74e4f47b051139b7a380036
msgid "Propagate the health change across all linked players"
msgstr "将生命值变化同步至所有关联玩家"

