msgstr "🛠️ 分步指南"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:32 d0e7f5af1be64d818cd0c529f69497f7
msgid "1. Prepare the Datapack"
msgstr "1. 准备数据包"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:34 53237cb0f1f247cb87eb2c105ee1dbe4
msgid ""
"First, we need a function that runs when your datapack is loaded. We'll "
"name it `lifestring:load` and register it in the `minecraft:load` tag. "
"This function will set up the necessary objectives."
msgstr ""
"首先创建数据包加载时运行的函数`lifestring:load`，"
"将其注册到`minecraft:load`标签中。"
"这个函数用于初始化记分板项。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:38 459521b0772943aca4b7bb1b4e873a44
msgid "**➔ create the `load` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 创建`load`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:40 ../../../examples/lifestring.md:99
#: 4221d5f21e354e2d96ba53ba25d92e66 85246a5e72fc44cb8dabffd36492fe3e
msgid "`@function lifestring:load`"
msgstr "`@function lifestring:load`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:46 fafdbccc69154923b4a6a068050e4923
msgid ""
"*`lifestring.link`*: Stores the link ID for each player. Players with the"
" same ID will share health."
msgstr ""
"*`lifestring.link`*：存储玩家链接ID。相同ID的玩家共享生命值。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:47 82a183a6793849edac49d4fb7e1d0b00
msgid ""
"*`lifestring.health`*: Stores each player's health from the previous "
"tick, so we can detect changes."
msgstr ""
"*`lifestring.health`*：存储玩家上一游戏刻的生命值，用于检测变化。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:49 7cd675813e0948aaad57124544237026
msgid "**➔ register it in the `load` tag**"
msgstr "**➔ 注册到`load`标签**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:51 8547cae026c948fdbc896f043d2181d3
msgid "`@function_tag minecraft:load`"
msgstr "`@function_tag minecraft:load`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:60 59fcd7acd4784bf080ccfaec60ee0d4c
msgid ""
"Adding `lifestring:load` to this tag ensures it runs automatically "
"whenever the datapack is enabled or reloaded."
msgstr ""
"将`lifestring:load`添加至此标签可确保数据包启用或重载时自动运行。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:64 6f84b673e59f4fb4b2999107f827ab43
msgid "2. Link Players Together"
msgstr "2. 建立玩家链接"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:67 59a360bf0a3c4ac5abe37e618884e103
msgid ""
"To make two players share health, they need the same *`lifestring.link`* "
"score. We'll create a function called `lifestring:create_link_ata`. The "
"\"ata\" part stands for \"as to at\", a Bookshelf convention for "
"functions that run in the context of one entity (*`as`*) while targeting "
"another (*`at`*). This makes it easy to link one player to another with a"
" single command:"
msgstr ""
"要使玩家共享生命值，需设置相同的*`lifestring.link`*分数。"
"创建`lifestring:create_link_ata`函数（“ata”代表“as to at”，即从执行者到执行位置，"
"是Bookshelf中表示在源实体(*`as`*)上下文操作目标实体(*`at`*)的命名规范），"
"通过单条命令链接玩家："

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:73 490085fa51d04706a2d121c0a6ae3ba8
msgid "**➔ create the `create_link_ata` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 创建`create_link_ata`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:75 79b86f9a8b0748048e43fd893b3f9685
msgid "`@function lifestring:create_link_ata`"
msgstr "`@function lifestring:create_link_ata`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:85 9bb0b4851f1846c8b57e02994b6fa4d4
msgid ""
"This function first check if the target player (*`@p`*) already has a "
"link ID. If not, it gives them a new one by incrementing a global "
"*`#counter`* score. Then, it copies that link ID from the target player "
"(*`@p`*) to the source player (*`@s`*)."
msgstr ""
"此函数首先检查目标玩家(*`@p`*)是否已有链接ID。"
"若无，则通过递增全局*`#counter`*分数分配新ID。"
"随后将目标玩家的链接ID复制至源玩家(*`@s`*)。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:89 0497a0e2ac1347bebdb2f70834f7ee70
msgid "3. Detect Health Changes"
msgstr "3. 检测生命值变化"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:91 d93340e313ca411db78d0dfcbca76335
msgid ""
"We need a function that constantly checks if a player's health has "
"changed. We'll create a function called `lifestring:tick` that schedules "
"itself every tick, and a function `lifestring:check` that runs for each "
"player."
msgstr ""
"需创建持续检测玩家生命值变化的函数："
"- `lifestring:tick`：每游戏刻自调度执行"
"- `lifestring:check`：为每个玩家执行"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:93 ad8c23dc0adb46358962920fdb11b337
msgid ""
"The `lifestring:check` function will compare the player's current health "
"to the health stored from the previous tick (*`@s lifestring.health`*). "
"If there's a difference, it will run `lifestring:change`."
msgstr ""
"`lifestring:check`函数比较玩家当前生命值与上一刻存储值(*`@s lifestring.health`*)。"
"若存在差异则运行`lifestring:change`。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:97 f2d7ff73c1a442309f671d19177195ff
msgid "**➔ update the `load` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 更新`load`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:106 3aa599012dd1472b8742ef64e0bd6566
msgid "**➔ create the `tick` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 创建`tick`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:108 0f503574415b4e2ea049f365b6d14b9d
msgid "`@function lifestring:tick`"
msgstr "`@function lifestring:tick`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:114 086f50bc1f944eb09b0d887e9aeb1e08
msgid "**➔ create the `check` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 创建`check`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:116 ed764a82846d46d28b3261bf3aa79633
msgid "`@function lifestring:check`"
msgstr "`@function lifestring:check`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:124 68321160ec7e49c5a4d120fb3688dc77
msgid ""
"We get the current health (with a scaling of 1000, which we'll use for "
"health in this system), then subtract the previous health to obtain the "
"difference in *`#this`*. If the score is not 0 then the health changed "
"and we run the change function. The second if check is here to ensure the"
" player has a *`lifestring.health`* score. Then we add this change to the"
" player's health score."
msgstr ""
"获取当前生命值（按1000倍缩放存储），"
"减去上一刻生命值得出*`#this`*中的变化量。"
"若非零则运行变更函数。"
"第二次条件检查确保玩家存在*`lifestring.health`*分数，"
"随后将变化量添加至玩家生命值分数。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:126 86ce94db18d448f9abc769dd5f8d1cf9
msgid "**➔ create the `change` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 创建`change`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:128 ../../../examples/lifestring.md:177
#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:187 ../../../examples/lifestring.md:206
#: 4e82bc3dd998463bbbfecce24caa1c7b 81b8c9e46cd842eb9cdef9ed92116429
#: 88eeb929493c481b938f2a40098204b5 cad001810a0548be889e2cba73b144f8
msgid "`@function lifestring:change`"
msgstr "`@function lifestring:change`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:133 37fe687c77f74365852315236ba231b3
msgid ""
"Now, whenever a linked player's health changes, the `lifestring:change` "
"function is triggered, and you'll see a message in chat from that player."
msgstr ""
"当关联玩家生命值变化时，`lifestring:change`函数触发，"
"该玩家将在聊天中发送消息。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:137 5e17e732108e484da51b96b624a58988
msgid "4. Find Linked Players"
msgstr "4. 查找关联玩家"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:139 7f425130e9ed4f7ea5c86363fee2b27f
msgid ""
"Now that we know when a player's health changes, we need to find all "
"other players who have the same *`lifestring.link`* score. We can do this"
" using a predicate."
msgstr ""
"已知玩家生命值变化时机，需查找具有相同*`lifestring.link`*分数的其他玩家。"
"可通过谓词实现。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:143 8d70408ed1d04c88a567c618b20ed5ea
msgid "**➔ create the `is_linked` predicate**"
msgstr "**➔ 创建`is_linked`谓词**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:145 ceece0c9eba9443d97b6634269a338e8
msgid "`@predicate lifestring:is_linked`"
msgstr "`@predicate lifestring:is_linked`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:173 3b04fbba7da645faa49fed9df1ec513c
msgid ""
"This predicate checks if the *`lifestring.link`* score of the entity "
"being evaluated (`\"this\"`) is equal to the *`lifestring.link`* score "
"stored in a temporary score named *`#this`*."
msgstr ""
"此谓词检查被评估实体(`\"this\"`)的*`lifestring.link`*分数"
"是否等于临时分数*`#this`*中存储的值。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:175 ../../../examples/lifestring.md:185
#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:204 1ebd68617c134bedb1f5861452c0e93d
#: 33ff1b843def406e972542b5bc33a130 4df14ba90a0949f08dcc851d677a92f9
msgid "**➔ update the `change` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 更新`change`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:183 cf1c5647639e47b1b9f63e26aa35f456
msgid ""
"Now, when a player's health changes, all linked players will say \"Health"
" Changed!\". However, we only want to update the health of the other "
"linked players, not the one whose health changed. To do this, we can "
"temporarily swap the *`#this`* score with the link ID of the player whose"
" health changed."
msgstr ""
"当玩家生命值变化时，所有关联玩家将发送\"生命值变化！\"消息。"
"但需仅更新其他关联玩家（排除变化源玩家）。"
"可通过临时交换*`#this`*分数与变化源玩家的链接ID实现。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:194 f98acc20e3f64147bff646db32b6be64
msgid ""
"The *`><`* operator swaps the scores. So, we first swap the *`#this`* "
"score with the player's link ID, then we find all linked players "
"(excluding the original player because their link ID is now in "
"*`#this`*), make them say the message, and then swap the scores back to "
"normal."
msgstr ""
"*`><`*运算符交换分数值："
"1. 将*`#this`*与玩家链接ID交换"
"2. 查找所有关联玩家（此时原玩家链接ID在*`#this`*中故被排除）"
"3. 发送消息"
"4. 交换回原始分数"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:198 db1600b79d2e4dc7a8ae4a4b683ee2b7
msgid "5. Update Players Health"
msgstr "5. 更新玩家生命值"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:200 266cf3c091834a5580a8cf45b497eb10
msgid ""
"Now we'll apply the health change to all the linked players. We'll do "
"this by using the health difference stored in *`#this`* and applying it "
"using Bookshelf's `#bs.health:add_health` function in a new "
"`lifestring:update` function."
msgstr ""
"将存储于*`#this`*的生命值变化量应用于所有关联玩家。"
"通过新建`lifestring:update`函数调用Bookshelf的"
"`#bs.health:add_health`实现。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:215 0c8b6dcd0a224a90ab94711f9277855a
msgid "**➔ create the `update` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 创建`update`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:217 ../../../examples/lifestring.md:227
#: 0cedbb388e444cd196797ba8362c9df7 daf44f12248242bd80f1cb22717cebf0
msgid "`@function lifestring:update`"
msgstr "`@function lifestring:update`"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:223 18d90f60b8b140e3a619e1a727a16201
msgid ""
"However, there’s a potential issue with this approach. The "
"`#bs.health:add_health` function cannot heal more than the player's "
"maximum health. Since we're not limiting the *`lifestring.health`* score,"
" we might run into trouble if it exceeds the player's max health. To "
"ensure this doesn’t happen, we need to define a maximum health value for "
"the score."
msgstr ""
"此方案存在潜在问题：`#bs.health:add_health`无法治疗超过玩家最大生命值。"
"由于未限制*`lifestring.health`*分数，可能超出最大值。"
"需定义分数上限值避免此问题。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:225 796b29fbbe8f47dbb8750358db794804
msgid "**➔ update the `update` function**"
msgstr "**➔ 更新`update`函数**"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:235 ee7fe32492f9404ba68c770ba8a4c4f1
msgid ""
"The *`<`* operator sets the score to the minimum value, ensuring *`@s "
"lifestring.health`* does not exceed *`#max lifestring.health`*."
msgstr ""
"*`<`*运算符将分数设为最小值，确保*`@s lifestring.health`*"
"不超过*`#max lifestring.health`*。"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:239 90a95f8cd603487fb6754b693efcf539
msgid "✔️ Conclusion"
msgstr "✔️ 结语"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:241 2db5186947154a49b1842fee4874e218
msgid ""
"The system is a great example of how Bookshelf simplifies tasks that "
"might otherwise seem complex. It now makes linked players share the "
"damage and healing they receive. But there are many ways you could make "
"this system even better! Here are some ideas to think about:"
msgstr ""
"本系统是Bookshelf简化复杂任务的典范，实现了关联玩家共享伤害与治疗。"
"你可通过以下方向进一步优化："

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:243 4a8a77e395e14cd39fbbfd257f1480f7
msgid ""
"**Different Starting Health:** What if linked players have different "
"amounts of health to begin with? Should they all end up with the same "
"health percentage, or the same exact health points?"
msgstr ""
"**差异化初始生命值**：若关联玩家初始生命值不同，应同步为相同百分比还是相同具体值？"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:244 30c01f8dfeec4b2db852e8679726fe2e
msgid ""
"**Maximum Health:** Should linked players add up their maximum health "
"together? If one player's max health changes (for example, from an effect"
" or item), how should that affect the others?"
msgstr ""
"**最大生命值**：是否累加关联玩家的最大生命值？若某玩家最大生命值变化（如药水效果），如何影响其他玩家？"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:245 05419133799d46819ae6150ca0a48e0a
msgid ""
"**Player Login:** What happens when a linked player leaves the game and "
"comes back? Should their health be saved and synced with the group?"
msgstr ""
"**玩家登录**：关联玩家退出后重进时，是否会保存生命值并与组内同步？"

#: ../../../examples/lifestring.md:247 41b0d9d0ba3243fbbd2d259df2722a8d
msgid ""
"Try experimenting with these ideas to make the lifestring system work the"
" way you want it to!"
msgstr "尝试实现这些构想，定制属于你的生命链接系统！"

